text: "I Don't Want to Be" is the debut single by Gavin DeGraw on his first album Chariot. The single was released in 2004. The song is in the Alternative rock genre. == Chart rankings == U.S. Billboard Hot 100 gave the single "I Don't Wanna Be" a ranking of #10, U.K. Singles Chart gave the single a ranking of #32, and Dutch Singles Chart ranked it at #9. == Discography == * "I Don't Wanna Be" (2004) * "Follow Through" (2004) * "Chariot" (2005) Category:2004 songs Category:Debut singles
title: I Don't Want to Be
